## Monorepo Structure

```
/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/          — React PWA (Vite), src/modules/{kiosk,cleaner,admin}
│   └── server/       — NestJS API, prisma/, Dockerfile
├── packages/
│   └── shared-types/ — Shared TS enums/types (src/index.ts, no tsconfig)
├── scripts/
