## Database Schema (Prisma)

**Models:** Organization → Building → Floor → Restroom → Device, User (with roles), Incident → IncidentAction, IssueType, KioskTemplate, CleanerArrival, PushSubscription

**Enums:** Gender (MALE/FEMALE/UNISEX), RestroomStatus (ACTIVE/INACTIVE/MAINTENANCE), DeviceType (KIOSK/SENSOR), UserRole (SUPER_ADMIN/ORG_ADMIN/MANAGER/SHIFT_SUPERVISOR/CLEANER), IncidentStatus (OPEN/IN_PROGRESS/RESOLVED), ActionType (REPORTED/ACKNOWLEDGED/RESOLVED/ESCALATED)

**Key relations:**
- Multi-tenant: Organization → Buildings → Floors → Restrooms → Devices
- User belongs to Organization, optionally assigned to Building
- Incident links Restroom + IssueType + Device + optional AssignedCleaner
- PushSubscription per user for Web Push notifications

