```
POSTGRES_PASSWORD, DATABASE_URL (postgresql://...)
REDIS_URL (redis://localhost:6379)
JWT_SECRET, JWT_REFRESH_SECRET, JWT_EXPIRES_IN (15m), JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN (7d)
NODE_ENV, PORT (3001), FRONTEND_URL
ADMIN_EMAIL, ADMIN_PASSWORD (seed defaults)
VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY, VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY
```

Server loads env from: `/opt/toilet-monitor/.env.production` → `.env.production` → `.env`

