## PWA Configuration

- **Strategy:** injectManifest (custom SW at `apps/web/src/sw.ts`)
- **Features:** precache, push notifications (VAPID), notification click handling
- **Manifest:** start_url `/cleaner`, standalone, portrait
- **VAPID public key:** hardcoded in `apps/web/src/lib/push.ts` (client-side)

