## Conventions

- **Commit style:** conventional commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `chore:`, `docs:`)
- **Language:** Hebrew UI with i18n (he/en), code in English
- **Push after every change** (see always-push.mdc rule)
- **Pre-push checks:** tsc --noEmit (server) + tsc -b (web) via Husky
- **PowerShell:** Use `-F` flag for commits (no heredoc support)
